    T - Type of object to read from or write to files

    public abstract class StringEncodeFileManager<T>
extends FileManager<T>
    Reads and writes Objects from raw text files.

    Note: Assumes StandardCharsets.ISO_8859_1 as Default Encoding
    Author:
